headline: Police chief: Extended anti-pullout road closures possible
description: Mass road-blocking protests during the upcoming pullout could mean that some roads would remain blocked for extended periods of time, Police Chief Moshe Karadi says. (Ilan Marciano)
articleBody: Mass road-blocking protests during the upcoming pullout could mean that some roads would remain blocked for extended periods of time, Police Chief Moshe Karadi says. (Ilan Marciano)
title: קפיצת מדרגה: גרמי מדרגות מפתיעים מהודו וסינגפור ועד ביירות וסיציליה
